            "date_published": "2021-11-26T06:44:04.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"纯h5-实现录音功能\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#纯h5-实现录音功能\">#</a> 纯 H5 实现录音功能</h2>\n<hr>\n<ul>\n<li>第一反应，则使用  <code>&lt;audio&gt;</code>  标签</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>定义和用法</strong><br/> <code>&lt;audio&gt;</code>  <em>标签定义声音，比如音乐或其他音频流。</em></p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;audio src&#x3D;&quot;&#x2F;i&#x2F;horse.ogg&quot; controls&#x3D;&quot;controls&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">Your browser does not support the audio element.</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;&#x2F;audio&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>创建一个<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9kZXZlbG9wZXIubW96aWxsYS5vcmcvZW4tVVMvZG9jcy9XZWIvQVBJL0F1ZGlvQ29udGV4dA==\"> AudioContext</span> 对象</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>AudioContext.createMediaStreamSource()</strong><br/><em>创建一个 MediaStreamAudioSourceNode 接口来关联可能来自本地计算机麦克风或其他来源的音频流 MediaStream。</em><br/><strong>AudioContext.createMediaStreamDestination()</strong><br/><em>创建一个 MediaStreamAudioDestinationNode (en-US) 接口来关联可能储存在本地或已发送至其他计算机的 MediaStream 音频。</em></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"-1-\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#-1-\">#</a> <figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">var audioCtx &#x3D; new AudioContext();</span><br><span class=\"line\">var source &#x3D; audioCtx.createMediaStreamSource(stream);</span><br><span class=\"line\">var destination &#x3D; audioCtx.createMediaStreamDestination();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></h2>\n<h4 id=\"试一试\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#试一试\">#</a> 试一试</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"../images/audio.html\">录音 demo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"../images/canvas.html\">手写 demo</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
